data.description: Sellers OFFERING 10K IN BUYER CONCESSIONS  Welcome Home, conveniently located near HWY 151 and Potranco. This well maintained open floor plan home is the perfect start for your family. Nearly 3,000 sqft with three living areas. You're greeted by the first family/dining room that leads into the spacious kitchen that over looks the second living space. Ideal for entertaining or hosting gatherings. The double doors that lead to the back yard that is privately fenced in, making it great for relaxation. The third living area located on the second floor has ample space for an office/entertainment space. The master suite has plenty of room for a sitting area and the restroom has been remodeled with a standup tile shower, double sink vanity and a walk-in closet. All rooms have ceiling fans, mature trees and two car garage. Price improvement and move in ready!
